# ERROR TIPS

### Errors when attempting to pickup non-existent items
- Verify the existence of items at target coordinates before attempting pickup
- Double check coordinates when trying to pickup specific resources

### Assertion errors for insufficient resources
- Ensure required resource quantities are available before proceeding with operations
- Implement proper resource checking before executing operations that require specific amounts

### Fuel-related issues
- Multiple entities are showing "out of fuel" warnings
- Ensure proper fuel distribution to burner entities
- Implement systematic fuel management for burner mining drills and inserters

### Entity placement and connection issues
- Steam engine showing "no input liquid" and "no fluid present in connections"
- Ensure proper pipe connections between power generation components
- Verify fluid flow path from offshore pump through boiler to steam engine

### Output blocking issues
- Some inserters are blocked due to full output containers
- Ensure proper item flow by managing container capacity
- Implement better output management systems
